{"Name":"Share Plugin","Id":2393,"Alias":"SharePlugin","Description":"# Share Plugin Details\r\n\r\nShare text, links, or open a browser in Xamarin.iOS, Xamarin.Android, Windows Phone, and Windows from a single API. \r\n         \r\n### Features:\r\n\r\n* Share Text\r\n* Share Link\r\n* Open Browser\r\n\r\nWorks completely from shared code or PCL projects.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Plugins for Xamarin at [http://xamarin.com/plugins](http://xamarin.com/plugins)","Version":"3.0.1","Summary":"Easily share text, links, or open a browse from shared code.","QuickStart":"# Getting Started with Share Plugin\r\n\r\n### API Usage\r\n\r\nCall **CrossShare.Current** from any project or PCL to gain access to APIs.\r\n\r\n**Share**\r\n```\r\n/// \u003csummary\u003e\r\n/// Simply share text on compatible services\r\n/// \u003c/summary\u003e\r\n/// \u003cparam name=\"text\"\u003eText to share\u003c/param\u003e\r\n/// \u003cparam name=\"title\"\u003eTitle of popup on share (not included in message)\u003c/param\u003e\r\n/// \u003creturns\u003eawaitable Task\u003c/returns\u003e\r\nTask Share(string text, string title = null);\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Open Browser**\r\n```\r\n/// \u003csummary\u003e\r\n/// Open a browser to a specific url\r\n/// \u003c/summary\u003e\r\n/// \u003cparam name=\"url\"\u003eUrl to open\u003c/param\u003e\r\n/// \u003creturns\u003eawaitable Task\u003c/returns\u003e\r\nTask OpenBrowser(string url);\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Share Link**\r\n```\r\n/// \u003csummary\u003e\r\n/// Share a link url with compatible services\r\n/// \u003c/summary\u003e\r\n/// \u003cparam name=\"url\"\u003eLink to share\u003c/param\u003e\r\n/// \u003cparam name=\"message\"\u003eMessage to share\u003c/param\u003e\r\n/// \u003cparam name=\"title\"\u003eTitle of the popup\u003c/param\u003e\r\n/// \u003creturns\u003eawaitable Task\u003c/returns\u003e\r\nTask ShareLink(string url, string message = null, string title = null);\r\n```\r\n","Hash":"d9a46439bf14194233fa6a82f5e4405f","TargetPlatforms":["ios","ios-un